<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Thex Mallet Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Befallen and kill Elf Skeletons until you retrieve the Mallet Head and the Mallet Hilt.<BR>
<BR>
2) Find and kill Commander Windstream. He is about level 20 or so.   He will drop the Mallet Stem.<BR>
<BR>
3) Put the Mallet Head and the Mallet Hilt into the Mallet Stem and press combine.  You will have the Thex Mallet.</div>
<BR>
