<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Heelin</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-04-04 12:13:31</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Killing Gix to get the note is not a viable option. I tried this twice (once myself, and another time I had a DE loot it and give it to Llrod..nothing.) You must be a Dark Elf Shadowknight (or some race/class combination that Gix likes, DE SK worked for me) and say to Gix "Utalk adarev otcin", and he should give you the note. Then give this note to skeleton Llrod, who spawns on the first level of befallen (second door on the right, near the well) every ten minutes or so, and Windstream will spawn. This is the ONLY way he will spawn as far as I know. He spawns somewhere on the third floor, possibly in front of the chair behind the illusionary wall. Elf skeletons spawn right behind the third floor door, and sometimes have a placeholder. Mallet head is common (got it three times), and hilt seems to be uncommon (got it once out of maybe 6 kills.) Good luck</font></td></tr></table>
